    "feat": {
        "name": "Animal Companion",
        "type": "stat_block_section",
        "subtype": "feat",
        "text": "You gain the service of a young animal companion that travels with you on your adventures and obeys any simple commands you give it to the best of its abilities. See Animal Companions for more information.  \n  \n**Ranger**: When you Hunt Prey, your animal companion gains the action's benefits and your hunter's edge benefit if you have one.",
